# Port Interface Registry
# This file documents all port interfaces and their implementations

## Database Ports
### DatabasePort
- Interface: src/shared/ports/database_port.py
- Description: Complete database operations for events and offsets
- Adapters:
  - PostgreSQL: src/infra/adapters/postgresql/postgres_adapter.py
  - MongoDB: src/infra/adapters/mongodb/mongo_adapter.py

### EventReaderPort
- Interface: src/shared/ports/database_port.py
- Description: Read events from database
- Adapters:
  - PostgreSQL: src/infra/adapters/postgresql/event_reader_adapter.py
  - MongoDB: src/infra/adapters/mongodb/event_reader_adapter.py

### EventManagementPort
- Interface: src/shared/ports/database_port.py
- Description: Manage event lifecycle operations
- Adapters:
  - PostgreSQL: src/infra/adapters/postgresql/event_management_adapter.py
  - MongoDB: src/infra/adapters/mongodb/event_management_adapter.py

### OffsetPort
- Interface: src/shared/ports/database_port.py
- Description: Manage consumer offsets
- Adapters:
  - PostgreSQL: src/infra/adapters/postgresql/offset_adapter.py
  - MongoDB: src/infra/adapters/mongodb/offset_adapter.py

### CountPort
- Interface: src/shared/ports/database_port.py
- Description: Count operations on events
- Adapters:
  - PostgreSQL: src/infra/adapters/postgresql/count_adapter.py
  - MongoDB: src/infra/adapters/mongodb/count_adapter.py

