## DI Configuration
- Container: src/shared/di/container.py
- Environment-based adapter selection
- Configuration: .env.example

## Port Implementation Rules
1. All adapters must implement exactly one port interface
2. Adapters contain zero business logic
3. Adapters wrap vendor calls in trace spans
4. Adapters map vendor errors to shared/errors/codes.yaml
5. Business logic uses ports only, never adapters directly
